snippet.title: TEVI - Official Gameplay Trailer | The MIX Next August 2023
snippet.description: Watch the latest trailer for Tevi to see gameplay, exploration, enemies, and more from this upcoming bullet hell Metroidvania game. Tevi will be available in Q3 2023 on PlayStation, Xbox, Nintendo Switch, and Steam.
